  "title": "Admin and Operations Officer",
  "description": "<p>5 Day Work Week</p><p>Walking distance from 2 MRTs</p><p>Working Timing: 9am – 6pm</p><p>Starting Salary $2300 - $2500</p><p>Job Description:</p><p>· Provide day-to-day office support</p><p>· Handle client’s enquiries through calls and email</p><p>· Handle client’s invoices in a timely manner</p><p>· Assist in processing and updating client’s data</p><p>· Data entry and preparation of daily/monthly reports</p><p>· Any other duties assigned.</p><p>· Able to speak Chinese as we have a lot of Chinese speaking clients</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>· Minimum Polytechnic Diploma in any discipline</p><p>· Proficient in Microsoft Office</p><p>· Pleasant personality</p><p>· Able to work well in a team</p><p>· Be proactive and able to take initiative</p><p>· Organized, meticulous with a high degree of accuracy</p><p>· Able to start work immediately or on a short notice will be advantageous.</p>",
